CREATE TABLE "__EFMigrationsHistory" (
    "MigrationId" TEXT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "PK___EFMigrationsHistory" PRIMARY KEY,
    "ProductVersion" TEXT NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE "AspNetRoles" (
    "Id" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "PK_AspNetRoles" PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
    "Name" TEXT NULL,
    "NormalizedName" TEXT NULL,
    "ConcurrencyStamp" TEXT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE "AspNetUserClaims" (
    "Id" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "PK_AspNetUserClaims" PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
    "UserId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "ClaimType" TEXT NULL,
    "ClaimValue" TEXT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_AspNetUserClaims_AspNetUsers_UserId" FOREIGN KEY ("UserId") REFERENCES "AspNetUsers" ("Id") ON DELETE CASCADE
)

CREATE TABLE "AspNetUserLogins" (
    "LoginProvider" TEXT NOT NULL,
    "ProviderKey" TEXT NOT NULL,
    "ProviderDisplayName" TEXT NULL,
    "UserId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT "PK_AspNetUserLogins" PRIMARY KEY ("LoginProvider", "ProviderKey"),
    CONSTRAINT "FK_AspNetUserLogins_AspNetUsers_UserId" FOREIGN KEY ("UserId") REFERENCES "AspNetUsers" ("Id") ON DELETE CASCADE
)

CREATE TABLE "AspNetUserTokens" (
    "UserId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "LoginProvider" TEXT NOT NULL,
    "Name" TEXT NOT NULL,
    "Value" TEXT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT "PK_AspNetUserTokens" PRIMARY KEY ("UserId", "LoginProvider", "Name"),
    CONSTRAINT "FK_AspNetUserTokens_AspNetUsers_UserId" FOREIGN KEY ("UserId") REFERENCES "AspNetUsers" ("Id") ON DELETE CASCADE
)

CREATE TABLE "Genres" (
    "Id" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "PK_Genres" PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
    "Name" TEXT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE "AspNetRoleClaims" (
    "Id" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "PK_AspNetRoleClaims" PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
    "RoleId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "ClaimType" TEXT NULL,
    "ClaimValue" TEXT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_AspNetRoleClaims_AspNetRoles_RoleId" FOREIGN KEY ("RoleId") REFERENCES "AspNetRoles" ("Id") ON DELETE CASCADE
)

CREATE TABLE "AspNetUserRoles" (
    "UserId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "RoleId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT "PK_AspNetUserRoles" PRIMARY KEY ("UserId", "RoleId"),
    CONSTRAINT "FK_AspNetUserRoles_AspNetRoles_RoleId" FOREIGN KEY ("RoleId") REFERENCES "AspNetRoles" ("Id") ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_AspNetUserRoles_AspNetUsers_UserId" FOREIGN KEY ("UserId") REFERENCES "AspNetUsers" ("Id") ON DELETE CASCADE
)

CREATE TABLE "BooksTable" (
    "Id" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "PK_BooksTable" PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
    "Title" TEXT NULL,
    "Author" TEXT NULL,
    "Description" TEXT NULL,
    "AboutAuthor" TEXT NULL,
    "GenreId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "Review" TEXT NULL, "Rating" REAL NOT NULL DEFAULT 0.0,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_BooksTable_Genres_GenreId" FOREIGN KEY ("GenreId") REFERENCES "Genres" ("Id") ON DELETE CASCADE
)

CREATE TABLE "BPhotos" (
    "Id" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "PK_BPhotos" PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
    "UrlBook" TEXT NULL,
    "IsMain" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "PublicId" TEXT NULL,
    "AppBooksId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_BPhotos_BooksTable_AppBooksId" FOREIGN KEY ("AppBooksId") REFERENCES "BooksTable" ("Id") ON DELETE CASCADE
)

CREATE TABLE "Followers" (
    "SourceUserId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "TargetUserId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT "PK_Followers" PRIMARY KEY ("SourceUserId", "TargetUserId"),
    CONSTRAINT "FK_Followers_AspNetUsers_SourceUserId" FOREIGN KEY ("SourceUserId") REFERENCES "AspNetUsers" ("Id") ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_Followers_AspNetUsers_TargetUserId" FOREIGN KEY ("TargetUserId") REFERENCES "AspNetUsers" ("Id") ON DELETE CASCADE
)

CREATE TABLE "Messages" (
    "Id" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "PK_Messages" PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
    "Content" TEXT NULL,
    "DateRead" TEXT NULL,
    "MessageSent" TEXT NOT NULL,
    "RecipientDeleted" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "RecipientId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "RecipientUsername" TEXT NULL,
    "SenderDeleted" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "SenderId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "SenderUsername" TEXT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_Messages_AspNetUsers_RecipientId" FOREIGN KEY ("RecipientId") REFERENCES "AspNetUsers" ("Id") ON DELETE RESTRICT,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_Messages_AspNetUsers_SenderId" FOREIGN KEY ("SenderId") REFERENCES "AspNetUsers" ("Id") ON DELETE RESTRICT
)

CREATE TABLE "Photos" (
    "Id" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "PK_Photos" PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
    "AppUserId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "IsMain" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "PublicId" TEXT NULL,
    "Url" TEXT NULL, "IsApproved" INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_Photos_AspNetUsers_AppUserId" FOREIGN KEY ("AppUserId") REFERENCES "AspNetUsers" ("Id") ON DELETE CASCADE
)

CREATE TABLE "AspNetUsers" (
    "Id" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "PK_AspNetUsers" PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
    "AccessFailedCount" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "City" TEXT NULL,
    "ConcurrencyStamp" TEXT NULL,
    "Country" TEXT NULL,
    "Created" TEXT NOT NULL,
    "DateOfBirth" TEXT NOT NULL,
    "Email" TEXT NULL,
    "EmailConfirmed" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "Gender" TEXT NULL,
    "Interests" TEXT NULL,
    "Introduction" TEXT NULL,
    "KnownAs" TEXT NULL,
    "LastActive" TEXT NOT NULL,
    "LockoutEnabled" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "LockoutEnd" TEXT NULL,
    "LookingFor" TEXT NULL,
    "NormalizedEmail" TEXT NULL,
    "NormalizedUserName" TEXT NULL,
    "PasswordHash" TEXT NULL,
    "PhoneNumber" TEXT NULL,
    "PhoneNumberConfirmed" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "SecurityStamp" TEXT NULL,
    "TwoFactorEnabled" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "UserName" TEXT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE "FavoriteBooks" (
    "SourceUserId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "TargetBookId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "AppUserId" INTEGER NULL,
    CONSTRAINT "PK_FavoriteBooks" PRIMARY KEY ("SourceUserId", "TargetBookId"),
    CONSTRAINT "FK_FavoriteBooks_AspNetUsers_AppUserId" FOREIGN KEY ("AppUserId") REFERENCES "AspNetUsers" ("Id"),
    CONSTRAINT "FK_FavoriteBooks_AspNetUsers_SourceUserId" FOREIGN KEY ("SourceUserId") REFERENCES "AspNetUsers" ("Id") ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_FavoriteBooks_BooksTable_TargetBookId" FOREIGN KEY ("TargetBookId") REFERENCES "BooksTable" ("Id") ON DELETE CASCADE
)

CREATE TABLE "Reviews" (
    "Id" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "PK_Reviews" PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
    "SenderId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "SenderUsername" TEXT NULL,
    "BookId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "BookTitle" TEXT NULL,
    "Content" TEXT NULL,
    "DateSent" TEXT NULL,
    "ReviewSent" TEXT NOT NULL,
    "SenderDeleted" INTEGER NOT NULL, "Rate" INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_Reviews_AspNetUsers_SenderId" FOREIGN KEY ("SenderId") REFERENCES "AspNetUsers" ("Id") ON DELETE RESTRICT,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_Reviews_BooksTable_BookId" FOREIGN KEY ("BookId") REFERENCES "BooksTable" ("Id") ON DELETE RESTRICT
)

CREATE TABLE "Ratings" (
    "Id" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "PK_Ratings" PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
    "BookId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "BookTitle" TEXT NULL,
    "Rate" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "RateSent" TEXT NOT NULL,
    "SenderId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "SenderUsername" TEXT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_Ratings_AspNetUsers_SenderId" FOREIGN KEY ("SenderId") REFERENCES "AspNetUsers" ("Id") ON DELETE RESTRICT,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_Ratings_BooksTable_BookId" FOREIGN KEY ("BookId") REFERENCES "BooksTable" ("Id") ON DELETE RESTRICT
)

CREATE TABLE "BooksReads" (
    "SourceUserId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "TargetBookId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "AppUserId" INTEGER NULL,
    CONSTRAINT "PK_BooksReads" PRIMARY KEY ("SourceUserId", "TargetBookId"),
    CONSTRAINT "FK_BooksReads_AspNetUsers_AppUserId" FOREIGN KEY ("AppUserId") REFERENCES "AspNetUsers" ("Id"),
    CONSTRAINT "FK_BooksReads_AspNetUsers_SourceUserId" FOREIGN KEY ("SourceUserId") REFERENCES "AspNetUsers" ("Id") ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_BooksReads_BooksTable_TargetBookId" FOREIGN KEY ("TargetBookId") REFERENCES "BooksTable" ("Id") ON DELETE CASCADE
)

CREATE TABLE "Reads" (
    "Id" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "PK_Reads" PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
    "SenderId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "SenderUsername" TEXT NULL,
    "BookId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "BookTitle" TEXT NULL, "ReadSent" TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT '0001-01-01 00:00:00',
    CONSTRAINT "FK_Reads_AspNetUsers_SenderId" FOREIGN KEY ("SenderId") REFERENCES "AspNetUsers" ("Id") ON DELETE RESTRICT,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_Reads_BooksTable_BookId" FOREIGN KEY ("BookId") REFERENCES "BooksTable" ("Id") ON DELETE RESTRICT
)

CREATE TABLE "Connections" (
    "ConnectionId" TEXT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "PK_Connections" PRIMARY KEY,
    "Username" TEXT NULL,
    "GroupName" TEXT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_Connections_Groups_GroupName" FOREIGN KEY ("GroupName") REFERENCES "Groups" ("Name")
)

CREATE TABLE "Comments" (
    "Id" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "PK_Comments" PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
    "SenderId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "SenderUsername" TEXT NULL,
    "ReviewId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "ReviewTitle" TEXT NULL,
    "Content" TEXT NULL,
    "DateSent" TEXT NULL,
    "CommentSent" TEXT NOT NULL,
    "SenderDeleted" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_Comments_AspNetUsers_SenderId" FOREIGN KEY ("SenderId") REFERENCES "AspNetUsers" ("Id") ON DELETE RESTRICT,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_Comments_Reviews_ReviewId" FOREIGN KEY ("ReviewId") REFERENCES "Reviews" ("Id") ON DELETE RESTRICT
)

CREATE TABLE "CommentLikes" (
    "SourceUserId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "TargetReviewId" INTEGER NOT NULL,
    "AppBooksId" INTEGER NULL,
    "AppUserId" INTEGER NULL,
    CONSTRAINT "PK_CommentLikes" PRIMARY KEY ("SourceUserId", "TargetReviewId"),
    CONSTRAINT "FK_CommentLikes_AspNetUsers_AppUserId" FOREIGN KEY ("AppUserId") REFERENCES "AspNetUsers" ("Id"),
    CONSTRAINT "FK_CommentLikes_AspNetUsers_SourceUserId" FOREIGN KEY ("SourceUserId") REFERENCES "AspNetUsers" ("Id") ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT "FK_CommentLikes_BooksTable_AppBooksId" FOREIGN KEY ("AppBooksId") REFERENCES "BooksTable" ("Id"),
    CONSTRAINT "FK_CommentLikes_Reviews_TargetReviewId" FOREIGN KEY ("TargetReviewId") REFERENCES "Reviews" ("Id") ON DELETE CASCADE
)
